biography.bio: Mariya Pirogova is an actress, known for Dark World 2: Equilibrium (2013), Interny (2010) and Superplokhie (2016).

biography.placeOfBirth: Chimkent, Chimkentskaya oblast, Kazakh SSR, USSR [now Shymkent, Ongtustik Qazaqstan oblysy, Kazakhstan]
biography.bio: Pavel Priluchnyy was born on November 5, 1987 in Chimkent, Chimkentskaya oblast, Kazakh SSR, USSR as Pavel Valerevich Priluchnyy. He is an actor, known for Zakrytaya shkola (2011), Taynyy gorod (2014) and Dark World 2: Equilibrium (2013). He has been married to Agata Mutsenietse since July 19, 2011. They have two children.
biography.name: Pavel Priluchnyy

biography.bio: Eugenia Khirivskaya was born on September 3, 1981 in Moscow, RSFSR, USSR as Evgeniya Vladimirovna Brik. She is an actress, known for Hipsters (2008), The Geographer Drank His Globe Away (2013) and Tiski (2007). She has been married to Valeriy Todorovskiy since 2006. They have one child.
biography.name: Eugenia Khirivskaya

biography.placeOfBirth: Ryazan, Ryazanskaya oblast, RSFSR, USSR [now Russia]
biography.bio: Vladislav Abashin was born on June 28, 1979 in Ryazan, Ryazanskaya oblast, RSFSR, USSR. He is an actor, known for In the Fog (2012), Zhila-byla odna baba (2011) and Reverse Motion (2010).

biography.placeOfBirth: Leningrad, RSFSR, USSR [now St. Petersburg, Russia]
biography.bio: Paulina Andreeva was born on October 19, 1988 in Leningrad, RSFSR, USSR as Paulina Olegovna Andreeva. She is an actress, known for Ottepel (2013), The Method (2015) and Dark World 2: Equilibrium (2013).
biography.name: Paulina Andreeva

biography.bio: Aleksandr Cherkasov is an actor, known for La chasse aux papillons (1992), Triple agent (2004) and Pravo na vystrel (1981).
biography.name: Aleksandr Cherkasov

biography.bio: Igor graduated in 1989 from the Leningrad Institute of Theatre, Music and Cinema. He is a member of the world renowned Maly Drama Theatre of Saint Petersburg, Russia, directed by Lev Dodin. Igor tours with the troupe performing MDT originals such as "Gaudeamus", "Claustrophobia", and an adaptation of Chekov's Platonov called "A Play Without a Name." He has several film credits to his name including the most recent "Koktebel" which was widely acclaimed in film festivals around the world.
biography.name: Igor Chernevich

biography.bio: Dmitriy Gorevoy is an actor, known for The Way (2009), Dark World 2: Equilibrium (2013) and Bachelor Party (2017).
biography.name: Dmitriy Gorevoy

biography.bio: Alisa Khazanova was born on February 13, 1974 in Moscow, RSFSR, USSR as Alisa Gennadevna Khazanova. She is an actress and director, known for The Woman in Black (2012), Conte de l'obscurité (2009) and I'll Be Around (2012). She has been married to Dmitry Shokhin since May 8, 2015. She was previously married to David Bauman.
biography.name: Alisa Khazanova

biography.bio: Kristina Kucherenko is an actress, known for Dark World 2: Equilibrium (2013), Dve sudby (2002) and Derevenskaya komediya (2009).
biography.name: Kristina Kucherenko

biography.bio: Valeriya Lanskaya was born on January 2, 1987 in Moscow, RSFSR, USSR as Valeriya Aleksandrovna Zaytseva. She is an actress, known for Tarif Novogodniy (2008), Rabbit Over the Void (2006) and Temporary Unavaliable (2015). She has been married to Stas Ivanov since March 1, 2015. They have one child.
biography.name: Valeriya Lanskaya
